This is the README for Lingua::EN::ABC version 0.12.

Lingua::EN::ABC is a "module" for the Perl computer programming language, a
library of computer code to install on a computer.  This document contains
four sections:

1. About - what the module does

2. Documentation - how to learn more about the module

3. Installation - how to install this module on a computer

4. Help - what to do if you get stuck

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. ABOUT

Lingua::EN::ABC - American, British, and Canadian English

This module offers functions to convert between the spellings and
vocabulary of American, British, and Canadian versions of English.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. DOCUMENTATION

You can read the documentation for the module online at the following
website:

    * http://metacpan.org/release/Lingua-EN-ABC

(This link goes to the latest version of the module.)

After installing the module, you can read the documentation on your
computer using

    perldoc Lingua::EN::ABC

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. INSTALLATION

This module requires Perl version 5.6.1 or later.

To install the module from CPAN, use

    cpan Lingua::EN::ABC

If you have the App::cpanminus installer, you may prefer

    cpanm Lingua::EN::ABC

To install the module from the source file, Lingua-EN-ABC-0.12.tar.gz,
follow this sequence of commands:

    tar xfz Lingua-EN-ABC-0.12.tar.gz
    cd Lingua-EN-ABC-0.12
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

If you want to test the module before installing it, use "make test" after
"make" and before "make install".

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. HELP

To get help with the module, you can email the author, Ben Bullock, at
<bkb@cpan.org>. If you think there is a problem in the module, you can
report a bug at 

<https://github.com/benkasminbullock/Lingua-EN-ABC/issues>,

or if you want to alter the source code of Lingua::EN::ABC, try the public
repository on github at 

<https://github.com/benkasminbullock/Lingua-EN-ABC>. 

